00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:57.320
For now, all we can do is

00:02:57.320 --> 00:02:58.880
alleviating her inflammation and pain.

00:02:58.880 --> 00:02:59.760
Beyond that,

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:02.690
