It's good to hear your voice,

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:53.120
Ms. Ye Haimeng.

00:09:53.680 --> 00:09:54.440
Your mother,

00:09:54.440 --> 00:09:55.070
Ms. Luo Yanxin,

00:09:55.070 --> 00:09:55.760
[Unknown number]

