Every asset

00:10:19.280 --> 00:10:20.880
under Ms. Luo Yanxin's name.

00:10:22.160 --> 00:10:22.800
Haimeng,

00:10:23.280 --> 00:10:24.280
that means

00:10:24.280 --> 00:10:25.520
your mother's shares

00:10:25.880 --> 00:10:27.340
